{"tid":454374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英智庫人權報告：京顛覆港法制","createTime":"2017-11-01T05:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T06:16:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8faca513a590aadd4df1a3a8130eb8d3674ae7b0","tid":454374,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:20:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171101/20200958\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171101%2F20200958&d=xuRX9uJAygzHR0L88SaOrwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=dc63e402\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171101%2F20200958&h=5a329080\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171101/20200958</a><br />\n<br />\n英智庫人權報告：京顛覆港法制<br />\n<br />\n5,120<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171101/large/18334847.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171101%2Flarge%2F18334847.jpg&h=e1808701&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■2014年推行國民教育，令雨傘運動崛起。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】英國智庫亨利傑克遜學會（Henry Jackson Society）昨發表香港人權報告，直指本港在過去20年人權狀況持續惡化，民主及法律權利在10年內大幅下跌。報告明言內地多次直接及間接顛覆本港的立法及司法制度，並提及近年推行的國民教育、警方濫權、人大釋法及銅鑼灣書店事件等。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171101/large/a0602a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171101%2Flarge%2Fa0602a.gif&h=b88184a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n指普選前景黯淡<br />\n<br />\n由英國智庫亨利傑克遜學會發表名為《香港二十年：公民、人權及法律權利倒退》的報告，內容提及本港97前及回歸至今的狀況，當中涉及政治、經濟、紅色資本、人權及法治等層面。報告指出，今年是香港回歸中國20年，距離特別行政區完結還有30年，但一國兩制已遭破壞，北京干預香港的制度及自主權，令經濟、政治及法律領域均受到影響。<br />\n<br />\n報告提到，英國政府最初要確保香港自主權，目的是要維持本港在金融上的成功，若沒有香港，中國的經濟發展不會如此迅速，然而本港的特殊地位正面臨威脅，中國現時反令本港經濟依賴內地。《基本法》雖保障香港司法獨立，但一國兩制根本上的矛盾，衝擊着香港的司法制度，並慢慢破壞本港法治、自由及人權。報告直言，北京進一步控制香港，本港普選前景黯淡，隨着反對聲音的空間逐步收窄、政治制度又被歪曲成是民主進步的錯覺，社會及市民日益感到沮喪及無望。<br />\n<br />\n報告分開9個章節，邀請了香港及英國學者及社運領袖撰寫，包括本土民主前線發言人梁天琦、最近獲保釋的香港眾志主席羅冠聰，以及時事評論人練乙錚等。<br />\n<br />\n其中羅冠聰的章節註明是在塘福懲教所服刑時撰寫的，他形容，在囚的兩個月間，體會到一個簡單的事實──香港自由正以近代史上最快的速度消失。<br />\n<br />\n■記者伍雅謙  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n赴英國會發言　梁天琦：兩制護港希望幻滅　報告指英方應確保聯合聲明落實<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n紀錄片競逐奧斯卡　入獄69日黃之鋒「現身」紐約<br />\n<br />\n赴英國會發言　梁天琦：兩制護港希望幻滅報告指英方應確保聯合聲明落實"},{"pid":"cd6e33284f95513cbfb0427c1309d501d18ff6b4","tid":454374,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69719751193b9e8dc002fe23f7ddb037b2c6de5","tid":454374,"uid":19213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T08:32:54.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cee419f1a252cea4ac2b66f6d2fb58eac300a73","tid":454374,"uid":56015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T08:39:14.000Z","msg":"原文<a href=\"http://henryjacksonsociety.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Hong-Kong-20-years.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhenryjacksonsociety.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2FHong-Kong-20-years.pdf&d=xuRX9uJAygzHR0L88SaOrwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=8131aaa6\" target=\"_blank\">http://henryjacksonsociety.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Hong-Kong-20-years.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"e791aa38a9ed51d729fa2fc21e31e04db0ce5915","tid":454374,"uid":95617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T08:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c05823bceab6f006a3cb1d665a8effb941c6091","tid":454374,"uid":22858,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T08:55:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">又係外國勢力</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><ins>細字濃縮試用版</ins><br />\n經crosscheck多個post，確信五毛名單臚列如下：三色貓、法國佬巫斯義、群龍共舞、優美開始、JR、RedBaron、Gladiclus、D_Wade、dewi、newlife、bbchu、十卜Ching、侵B、吾系甘開心牙、返六日唔撚易、毛澤東<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<ins>證據一：五毛一見字眼空群而出</ins><br />\n連狗對五毛問題視而不見、置若罔聞，與全連登作對<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451623\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451623</a><br />\n【枕戈待旦】有關被連狗封鎖禁言之嚴正聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/442843\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/442843</a><br />\n刺刀捅向習匪頭 鏟平地獄鬼國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/439819\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/439819</a><br />\n【黑暗】濕鳩塞鷗兄已遭連尼住禁言七日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/435231\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/435231</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>證據二：五毛擾亂視聽妖言惑眾</ins><br />\nJR：(人手置頂) 屈毛黨名單<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/405731\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/405731</a><br />\nRedBaron：關愛座呢隻五毛都算高招<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451674\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451674</a><br />\nGladiclus：（大踢爆）關愛座hunter係5毛！被bam屈毛派親身指證！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451720\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451720</a><br />\nJR：要求admin立即ban左三位會員︰關愛座hunter, 濕鳩塞鷗, 1000歲人瑞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451747\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451747</a><br />\nRedBaron（已改名）：香港獨立之後一定要實行獨裁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/452801\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/452801</a></strong></span>"},{"pid":"985ab77785b27d0f7e029210d08e522ca500a5a6","tid":454374,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T10:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7879585